title: Other Securities, Bank of England for Great Britain
notes:
Data For 1844-September 1857 Are For The Last Saturday Of The Month; All Other Data Are For Next To Last Saturday And Last Wednesday Of The Month. Data For 1888-1907 Were Checked With Volume 21 Of The National Monetary Commission. Data For 1862-1864, 1884, 1896-1897, 1906, 1914, March 1919, And November 1924 Were Checked With The Economist (London). Misprints Were Found In The Data From Bankers' For March 1919 And November 1925. Data For November 1928-1935 Were Computed By NBER From "Other Securities" Plus "Discounts And Advances". Source: Bankers' Magazine.

This NBER data series m14083 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
